<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[زَلِزَ]</span>: الزَّلَزُ: القلق.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[ع]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[زَلَعَ]</span>: الزَّلَعُ: تَفَطُّر الجلد، قال الخليل <span class="c2">«٤»</span>: الزَّلَعُ: تشققُ ظاهر الكف.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وإِن كان في الباطن فهو:</span> كَلَعٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
